1949;;The Undercover Man;;American;;Joseph H. Lewis;;Glenn Ford, Nina Foch, James Whitmore;;crime drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Undercover_Man;;Frank Warren is a treasury agent assigned to put an end to the activities of a powerful mob crime boss. The agent struggles to put together a case but is frustrated when all he finds are terrified witnesses and corrupt police officers. Although most informants end up dead, Agent Warren gets critical information about the mob from an unlikely source.